description:
Ise Nanao is the vice-captain of the eighth protection squad. Unlike her carefree captain, http://anidb.net/ch7197 [Kyouraku], Nanao is very serious and she often has to keep her superior in check. She also has to deflect Kyouraku`s attempted flirtations and teasing, usually by hitting him with something or scolding him.
Source: Anime-Planet
name: Ise Nanao
